asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

name: Ahi Okelani
description:
Hi everyone!

Im Ahi Okeelani. A rather interesting name I know! Okelani is our tribal lineage and is Hawaiian meaning From Heaven or from the blue skies. There are only 3 of us down here in the Underground with this bright blue pelt - many of them descendants of this Okelani lineage. And Ahi means Fire - mum and dad named me this due to my fiery red hair and according to them because my passion and sass as well! I guess I can count my blessings - im one of only 100 out of 10000 down here in the Underground with red hair! But im the only one that I know of down here with a red mane and bright blue body so I feel quite special about that.

Prior to the Wreck I was an entertainer, songstress and musical muse for virtually every Fluf gathering, party and congregation. Im only young, but I can play 25 different instruments - find another Fluf that can do that! An integral part of our life mission here in Fluf World is to provide total Happiness to every Fluf, so im blessed to do what I do.

My goal in Life is to one day find my Prince Charming, my Fluf soulmate, to start a beautiful family of our own. I know we will connect one day xo

name: Afterburner
description: Hey team, you got to get on board this ride, we are going to take things to the next level at the upcoming festivals. Im very experienced in this so just follow my lead and everything will work out incredible. Preparation is key, I have ex military training, then post service I have REALLY started living, connecting with fluf world of all walks of life, opening up my mind, getting involved, putting in the effort, and giving, giving, giving. It really is true, the universe will provide and the universal law of attraction will give you what you need. So if you want something, start giving it, and it will come back to you eventually. But you have to have faith and do it without expectation. Thats where these festivals like Burning Man really open you up to the possibilities of what fluf world could be like. You wont be any happier earning more. Be happy in the now, now is life, right at this moment. Thats why we have met. Here, eat this piece of paper, Im gonna show you the time of your life. Lets burn!

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

name: Tisha Harelor
description:
**Tisha Taylor**
Charlie Flurphy and Tisha Harelor were soul mates, as Charlie explained it, saying, "For me, it was an instant. The first night I met Tisha was on a boat. She was having dinner with her friends. She didn’t know who I was, and I asked her to come with me. Her friends told her not to go. But she did." He continued, “We drove straight to my brother’s house.  My mother was there. My stepfather was there. Eddie was there. They were all in the kitchen. I walked in and said, ‘This is my future wife.'”

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle.

name: Schnapps
description: One can tell by his demeanour that his atti tude may be a little schnappy. A tough upbringing by parents who suffered trauma, he still carries the stories he made about himself from things that happened, and runs rackets in his mind confirming the thoughts his ego tells him, making meaning out of the smallest things. After a few tipples of his favourite drink, you guessed it, hes the life of the party, forgetting his worries, sedating his ego and allowing him to act how he wants to be. Say something nice and youre his best friend, say something that triggers his stories and he schnapps. Like all tough guys, Schnapps does have a heart and even though he may not realise it just wants to feel good enough, feel valued, feel he is loved, but keeps sabotaging relationships because he doesnt truly believe it, yet. His hard attitude and lack of care has brought him a long way in terms of carrots, but true happiness will always be beyond reach until he lets go of his stories and begins to love himself. The fluf community is a beautiful family and I see a beautiful future of Schnapps accepting himself, fur and all.

name: Indigo
description: Hey Flufs! Im Indigo. Im pretty much a regular fluf but am being mentored by my elders to make sure I stay on the right track. I hang out with them on some epic adventures all around flu world, on the D Low. You wouldnt believe me if I told you what we get up to. Its pretty exciting stuff. You could kinda say that we are diplomats of the mind, but we try to blend into normal society at the same time? Thats all I can say. Legend has it that Amethyst Eyes were developed over millennia by those that lived in burrows located in areas of extremely high mycelium. Their eyes glow purple and they feel extremely grounded and connected to the universe and all species. After the wreck, the abundant mycelium stocks were destroyed and very few sacred locations are now known. And most definitely nowhere one could have a burrow. Those with purple eyes go by many names, Amethyst Eyes, The Mycyliated, The Seers, The Enlightened, The Prescients, among others. They have extraordinary abilities such as strong telepathy between each other, mild telepathy with those without, the ability to alter the mood of others, and the ability to feel when something is going to happen, before it happens. They, are seemingly always plugged in to the mycelium network. Some see it as a blessing, while for those all-knowing, it is a sacred guardianship one must master and respect. Some have been lost from overwhelming voices and emotions circulating their minds. We are, The Seers.

description:
We fought for a better world and I cherish every moment I had with Jim. Rest in peace Jimmy.
